→ A window opens. Select the storage location on your computer.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>The vCard is available at the selected storage location.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="455">3.12. Reloading the contact data record</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can reload the data of the contact data record with one click.</p>
</div>
