<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="2000">12.2. Editing bank details</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can update the bank details of your contact at any time.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Editing bank details:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>CRM » Contacts</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Search (<span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-search  "></i></span>) the contact by means of the filter settings as described in the <a href="/en/crm/managing-contacts#200">Searching for a contact</a> chapter.<br>
→ The contacts that correspond to the search criteria entered are displayed.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click in the line of the contact.<br>
→ The detail view of the contact opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Bank details</strong> on the left side in the context menu.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Edit</strong> (<span class="icon yellow"><i class="fa fa-pencil  "></i></span>) in the card of the bank details that you want to edit.<br>
→ The bank data record opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Carry out the desired settings. Note <a href="#table-bank-details-contact">Table 15</a>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p><strong>Save</strong> (<span class="icon green"><i class="fa fa-save  "></i></span>) the settings.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect2">
<h3 id="2100">12.3. Deleting bank details</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Delete the bank details of your contact if the data is outdated.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph instruction">
<p>Deleting bank details:</p>
</div>
<div class="olist arabic">
<ol class="arabic">
<li>
<p>Go to <strong>CRM » Contacts</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Search (<span class="icon blue"><i class="fa fa-search  "></i></span>) the contact by means of the filter settings as described in the <a href="/en/crm/managing-contacts#200">Searching for a contact</a> chapter.<br>
→ The contacts that correspond to the search criteria entered are displayed.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click in the line of the contact.<br>
→ The detail view of the contact opens.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Bank details</strong> on the left side in the context menu.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Delete</strong> (<span class="icon red"><i class="fa fa-minus-square  "></i></span>) in the bank data record that you want to delete.<br>
→ A window appears and you need to confirm your decision.</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>Click on <strong>Delete</strong> (<span class="icon red"><i class="fa fa-minus-square  "></i></span>).<br>
→ The bank details are deleted and removed from the overview.</p>
</li>
</ol>
</div>
</div>
